ve act of the fifth day of Creation week. Gen. </div><div class="t m45b x11 ha y5d8 ff6 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1:20-23. </div><div class="t m45c x68 h29 y5d9 ff6 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">43 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
